of us who want

00:38:49.725 --> 00:38:52.570
to change the medical
model and want to see it

00:38:52.570 --> 00:38:54.280
more accessible to more folks.

00:38:54.280 --> 00:38:56.975
So I think that is
a definite goal.

00:38:56.975 --> 00:38:59.350
And something that you asked
me earlier, what gets me out

00:38:59.350 --> 00:39:00.170
