00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:06.580
of the doctor was right.

00:41:06.580 --> 00:41:09.130
I'm going to do what the
doctor said and Pharma is best.

00:41:09.130 --> 00:41:10.480
That's their generation.

00:41:10.480 --> 00:41:13.670
So they believe-- and their
medicine is transactional.

00:41:13.670 --> 00:41:16.510
You go to the doctor, you
get a script in your hand,

00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:17.890
that visit is now complete.

00:41:17.890 --> 00:41:19.390
If you did not get
a script in your,

00:41:19.390 --> 00:41:21.140
there's no point to the visit.

00:41:21.140 --> 00:41:23.300
So that's the generation
that they came from.

00:41:23.300 --> 00:41:24.710
So it's much more challenging.

00:41:24.710 --> 00:41:28.210
So the best way to start is two
or three things, I've noticed.

00:41:28.210 --> 00:41:31.150
Like, hey, why don't you just
try doing these two things?

00:41:31.150 --> 00:41:33.130
And not give them
too much information.

00:41:33.130 --> 00:41:34.810
I've actually seen
the reverse work.

00:41:34.810 --> 00:41:36.401
Like somebody our
age or younger,

00:41:36.401 --> 00:41:37.900
they want the
information, they want

00:41:37.900 --> 00:41:39.483
to understand how
everything connects.

00:41:39.483 --> 00:41:41.929
They want to be empowered
and an advocate.

00:41:41.929 --> 00:41:43.720
The older generation
doesn't want all that.

00:41:43.720 --> 00:41:47.140
They don't care about the
connection and the big words

00:41:47.140 --> 00:41:49.157
like inflammation
and oxidative stress.

00:41:49.157 --> 00:41:50.740
They're not interested
in any of that.

00:41:50.740 --> 00:41:53.440
All they want to know is
almost that same transactional

00:41:53.440 --> 00:41:54.970
language.

00:41:54.970 --> 00:41:57.220
Your joints hurt, try this.

00:41:57.220 --> 00:41:59.230
And then you give
them two things to do.

00:41:59.230 --> 00:42:00.850
And then you follow
back up, maybe

00:42:00.850 --> 00:42:03.620
after, give them two weeks,
and see if after two weeks,

00:42:03.620 --> 00:42:06.430
they were able to put those
two things into effect.

00:42:06.430 --> 00:42:08.860
So I would think--

00:42:08.860 --> 00:42:10.910
transactional is only word
that comes to my mind,

00:42:10.910 --> 00:42:12.790
but simple commands.

00:42:12.790 --> 00:42:13.940
This hurts, do this.

00:42:13.940 --> 00:42:15.310
That's not working, try this.

00:42:15.310 --> 00:42:17.290
Do this-- I've noticed
that anytime I sit with

00:42:17.290 --> 00:42:20.350
my mother-in-law,
my mom, or my dad--

00:42:20.350 --> 00:42:20.884
any of them.

00:42:20.884 --> 00:42:23.050
And they're all so different
in their personalities.

00:42:23.050 --> 00:42:24.190
But, essentially,
the conversation

00:42:24.190 --> 00:42:25.270
always goes the same way.

00:42:25.270 --> 00:42:27.850
Anytime I try to
connect the dots,

00:42:27.850 --> 00:42:30.850
put the pieces of their health
together, explain all of this,

00:42:30.850 --> 00:42:33.750
I lose / So, don't do that.

00:42:33.750 --> 00:42:35.710
Just be very simple
and be very direct.

00:42:35.710 --> 00:42:36.910
And see if they feel better.

00:42:36.910 --> 00:42:38.710
And oftentimes
they'll get results.

00:42:38.710 --> 00:42:40.915
And then that motivates
them to move on to step two

00:42:40.915 --> 00:42:42.430
or to step three.

00:42:42.430 --> 00:42:44.247
So try that.

