00:45:39.010 --> 00:45:43.780
But checking like a CRP,
ESR, which is a sed rate,

00:45:43.780 --> 00:45:44.620
and a homocysteine.

00:45:44.620 --> 00:45:46.750
Those three things you should
be doing every six months.

00:45:46.750 --> 00:45:48.580
Because to me, those are
the earliest warnings

00:45:48.580 --> 00:45:50.996
that something is wrong with
your body and something's not

00:45:50.996 --> 00:45:51.584
