the conventional range,

00:46:25.630 --> 00:46:27.760
but you feel like crap,
then we can go look back.

00:46:27.760 --> 00:46:29.260
And say, oh, no,
no that's not where

00:46:29.260 --> 00:46:30.740
your TSH needs to be for you.

00:46:30.740 --> 00:46:33.187
So I think tracking
this data, tracking

00:46:33.187 --> 00:46:35.020
these labs, that's the
beauty of technology,

00:46:35.020 --> 00:46:37.870
is tracking it over the
course of your lifespan.

00:46:37.870 --> 00:46:40.240
And knowing where you felt
great, where you didn't feel

00:46:40.240 --> 00:46:41.050
so good.

